message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) tasks such as Question Generation (QG) and Question Answering (QA). Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as NLP is a subfield of AI, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the proposed model is a machine learning-based approach, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as QA is a subfield of IR, and "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) as some QA tasks involve visual question answering.
